news_header: Veterinarians euthanized stranded small-sword whales after failed rescue attempts in Tasmania.
news_original_title: Noin sata valasta joudutaan lopettamaan Australiassa rantautumisen takia
news_text: A group of veterinarians and biologists attempted to rescue stranded small-sword whales in Tasmania, but after unsuccessful efforts, they decided to euthanize the surviving animals due to prolonged suffering. The cause of the mass stranding remains unclear.
